reviewText: Steve Winter, a proven cult leader with no real following, has posted these videos all over the place so you can see them free of charge. However why bother? The musicianship is amateurish at best and the production quality is atrocious.

Another great DVD from Winterband. These guys can really play and get the message of every song to the listener. I always have one of thier songs playing in my head as I go thru my day. I highly recommend thier music/DVD's.
